{"title":"For Berd Spokes: Erase Components Road and MTB Hook Flange Hubs","link":"https://theradavist.com/erase-components-berd-hook-flange-hubs/","date":1739887216000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=16dc943f-77f1-4f16-874c-9b29a20c9e51&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fberdspokes.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Berd Spokes</a> licenses its patented “hook” hub flange design to small manufacturers. One of which is Belgium-based <a href=\"https://www.erasecomponents.com/hook-flange-hubs\" target=\"_blank\">Erase Components</a> that offers made in Belgium road and MTB Hook Flange Hubs…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Erase_Components_Hook_Hubs.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Made from 7075T6 aerospace aluminum, Erase’s MTB hubs feature a titanium freehub, weigh 357 grams for the pair (371.90 €), with the rear utilizing 60 points of engagement with a 6º engagement. Also made from 7075T6 aerospace aluminium, Erase’s road hubs feature a titanium freehub, weigh 327 grams for the pair (314.05 €) and 36 points of engagement with a 10º engagement. Both MTB and road hubs come in four color options and various driver designs.</p>\n<p>Check out the full Erase Components line at <a href=\"https://www.erasecomponents.com/hook-flange-hubs\" target=\"_blank\">its website</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/erase-components-berd-hook-flange-hubs/\">For Berd Spokes: Erase Components Road and MTB Hook Flange Hubs</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"4fac31d4af73e25391a93a4da1701df93bd7e1ccb8ca82e68cdaf66d181d5271","category":"Cycling"}